{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"703809ae24","title":"毛泽东谈中国共产党是全中国人民的领导核心","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d312bf49cb","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":25,"articleId":"703809ae24"}],"tags":[{"id":"8ed7cf8c42","name":"编纂《毛泽东选集》第五卷","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b83357b8c7","type":"title","text":"毛泽东谈中国共产党是全中国人民的领导核心","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"},{"id":"a72675cb5b","type":"paragraph","text":"你们的会议开得很好。希望你们团结起来，作为全国青年的领导核心。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"},{"id":"7f23344165","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共产党是全中国人民的领导核心。没有这样一个核心，社会主义事业就不能胜利。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"},{"id":"ba004ea90b","type":"paragraph","text":"你们这个会议是一个团结的会议，对全中国青年会有很大的影响。我对你们表示祝贺。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"},{"id":"07529909b0","type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，团结起来，坚决地勇敢地为社会主义的伟大事业而奋斗。一切离开社会主义的言论行动是完全错误的。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"},{"id":"8b3ec25ded","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：根据《毛泽东选集》第五卷打印。但据会议参加者会议，毛泽东当时并没有说过“一切离开社会主义的言论行动是完全错误的” 此类的话。后者是根据反右的需要后来加上去的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24"}],"page":{"id":"f8ac9397c4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"703809ae24","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}